, serif;\">本實驗室陳世穎老師、陳弘明老師獲行政院農業委員會「農民福利制度規畫之研究」研究計畫</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxMsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 27px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"ecxMsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 27px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">合作單位</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">行政院農業委員會</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">計畫名稱</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:99</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">年度「農民福利制度規畫之研究」計畫</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">計畫主持人</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">林秀霞</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">共同主持人</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">陳世穎副教授、陳弘明助理教授、黃美玲講師、王財驛講師</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">研究目的</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:<br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">進入</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">世紀資訊爆炸的時代，資訊技術的發展是國家競爭力的表徵，</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">農業發展為國家帶來的經濟便是一個國家最扎根的基礎，而如何防治農</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">業天然災害帶給農業的損失，便是一個重大的議題，本計畫乃基於上述</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">之科學技術發展趨勢，選擇以資訊科技與農業天然災害等主題為探究的</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">主軸，期望經本計畫之研究，來提升農業</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">e</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">化，並為農業天然災害防治帶</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">來幫助本研究企圖以資訊科技與應用之觀點，利用</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">3S(GPS</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">GIS</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">、</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">RS)</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">技</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">術做為工具，將農業天然災害問題解決，是本計畫之研究目的。</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">計畫時程</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:99</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日至</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">99</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">年</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">月</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">日</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /><br style=\"line-height: 27px;\" /></span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">計畫編號</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">:</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">研建字</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px;\" lang=\"EN-US\">99047B</span><span style=\"line-height: 27px; font-family: 新細明體, serif;\">號</span></p>\r\n</span></p>','',1,0,0,7,'2011-09-30 10:10:15',42,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2011-09-30 10:10:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\"}',1,0,61,'',